msgid "In this level, we present the 'I am a knave' puzzle.\n"
"\n"
"The given islander §0 says 'I am a knave'\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"The goal is to prove §2. Given the rules of the game, and that §3 says 'I am a knave' we have a contradiction.\n"
